    <item>
      <title>当投资者专注于挥之不去的财政挑战时，镀金下降了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/uk-bonds-fall-as-investors-focus-on-lingering-fiscal-challenges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国的债券下降了，在周三宣布一项超出预期的债务计划之后删除了收益，因为投资者将注意力转移到了该国仍在不利的财务上，并在全球范围内增加了借贷成本的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/uk-bonds-fall-as-investors-focus-on-lingering-fiscal-challenges</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 10:37:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
